Company Overview of L-3 Communications Security and Detection Systems, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
L-3 Communications Security and Detection Systems, Inc. provides security detection systems. Its products include advanced personnel and aviation checkpoint screening solutions, cargo screening systems, explosives detection systems, explosives trace detection products, metal detectors, and X-ray systems. The company also offers maintenance and support services, including training, technical support, in-house repair, and spare parts services. Its products are used in advanced personnel, air cargo, aviation checkpoint, checked baggage, and critical infrastructure screening, as well as cargo and border security applications. The company offers its products through a sales and distribution netwo...
L-3 Communications Security and Detection Systems, Inc. provides security detection systems. Its products include advanced personnel and aviation checkpoint screening solutions, cargo screening systems, explosives detection systems, explosives trace detection products, metal detectors, and X-ray systems. The company also offers maintenance and support services, including training, technical support, in-house repair, and spare parts services. Its products are used in advanced personnel, air cargo, aviation checkpoint, checked baggage, and critical infrastructure screening, as well as cargo and border security applications. The company offers its products through a sales and distribution network in the United States and internationally. The company was incorporated in 1989 and is headquartered in Woburn, Massachusetts with additional offices in the United Kingdom, Singapore, the United Arab Emirates, China, and Australia. L-3 Communications Security and Detection Systems, Inc. operates as a subsidiary of L-3 Communications Holdings Inc.
